msgid "Vanus,"
"\n"
"\nThese recent visions have attracted unwanted attention. First they surrounded my dwelling, then they tracked me to this place I assumed was safe. I should never have come here."
"\n"
"\nRemember the messages I sent you in the past, always rife with elements of surprise? Our talks were like a ritual to me. I hope you find them in the proper order."
