#: 21337012-0-361
msgctxt "21337012-0-361"
msgid "A nereid stole my husband "
"\nMy husband a nereid stole"
"\nBeware the maids of the seastrand"
"\nLest you be the next we console."
"\n"
"\nWe strolled blithely along the shore"
"\nGathering shells and turning stones"
"\nWhen came the voice I now deplore"
"\nA voice, a song, such soaring tones!"
"\n"
"\nAt once, my husband quickly sped"
"\n"Wait!" I cried, "'Tis a nereid!""
"\nBut faster still he pressed ahead"
"\nHer sweet call could not be gainsaid."
"\n"
"\nToo late, alas, alas, too late"
"\nI found him swaying, deep in thrall"
"\nMy worst fear sent to me by fate"
"\nHe followed the nereid's call."
"\n"
"\nAnd she, beautiful, cruel, and vain"
"\nSwam to her sisters, calling this back,"
"\n"Your husband was no prize to gain;"
"\nHe's yours once more, Lady Crookback!""
"\n"
"\nA nereid stole my husband "
"\nReturning him without delay"
"\nPoor me, near free from his demands"
"\nStuck instead with him since that day!"
msgstr "ネレイドが私の夫を奪った\\r"
"\n私の夫をネレイドが奪った\\r"
"\n海辺の乙女には用心して\\r"
"\n次にあなたが慰められないように。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n私たちは無邪気に海岸をぶらついて\\r"
"\n貝を集めたり石をひっくり返したり\\r"
"\nそして声が聞こえ今の私は嘆く\\r"
"\nその声、歌は、あんなに高い声で！\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nすぐに夫は足を速めた\\r"
"\n「待って」私は叫んだ「ネレイドよ」\\r"
"\nしかし夫はさらに足を速めた\\r"
"\n彼女の甘い呼び声には逆らえない。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n手遅れだ、ああ悲しいかな、もう遅い\\r"
"\n彼の心は傾き、もう深い虜\\r"
"\n私の恐れは運命のように現実に\\r"
"\n彼はネレイドの呼び声に従った。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nそして彼女は美しく残酷で無分別\\r"
"\n姉妹の元へ泳ぎながら叫んだ\\r"
"\n「あなたの夫はつまらない\\r"
"\n返してあげるわ、背中曲がりの奥さん！」\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nネレイドが夫を奪って\\r"
"\nすぐに返してきた\\r"
"\nかわいそうな私、あの日から\\r"
"\n望まれないのに彼の側にいる！"

