#: 21337012-0-358
msgctxt "21337012-0-358"
msgid "Collected by Telenger the Artificer"
"\n"
"\nVulkwasten, widely known for its fermented beverages, is home to some of the friendliest Bosmer I've ever met. Like most of their kind, they are industrious and get along well with most people. After completing research into their brewing methods, I stayed overnight with a local family."
"\n"
"\nAs a historian, I realize one can learn much about a culture by studying its humor. Therefore, I copied down several of their witticisms for future examination. Perhaps by considering their amusements, we will gain further insight into the mind of the Bosmer."
"\n"
"\nA skeleton walks into the tavern and says, "I'd like some rotmeth. And a mop.""
"\n"
"\nQ: Why did the monkey fall out of the tree?"
"\nA: It was dead."
"\n"
"\nQ. What's brown and sticky?"
"\nA. A stick."
"\n"
"\nPerson One: Ask me if I'm a tree."
"\nPerson Two: Are you a tree?"
"\nPerson One: No."
"\n"
"\nQ. Which side of a raven has the most feathers?"
"\nA. The outside."
"\n"
"\nQ. What has three heads, is ugly, and smells?"
"\nA. My mistake! You don't have three heads!"
"\n"
"\nQ. What's light as a feather, but cannot be held for very long?"
"\nA. Breath."
"\n"
"\nQ. Imagine your boat's sinking in slaughterfish-infested waters. How do you survive?"
"\nA. Stop imagining!"
"\n"
"\nQ. Why do thunderbugs eat raw meat?"
"\nA. They never learned to cook."
"\n"
"\nQ. Why do bees buzz?"
"\nA. Because they can't whistle."
msgstr "発明家テレンジャーによる収集\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n発酵飲料で広く知られるバルクワステンには、知る中でも特に気さくなボズマーが暮らしている。種族の特徴でもあるが、彼らは勤勉でたいていの人とうまく付き合える。彼らの醸造方法の調査を終え、地元の家に泊めてもらった。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n歴史家として私は、ユーモアを研究すればその文化の多くを学べると考えている。そこで将来の研究のために彼らのジョークを書き留めておく。彼らの娯楽をよく知ればきっと、ボズマーの考え方をより深く理解できるだろう。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nスケルトンが酒場に入ってきてこう言ったんだ。「ロトメスをくれ。あとモップも」\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nQ: なぜ猿が木から落ちたか？\\r"
"\nA: 死んでたから。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nQ. 茶色くてボーッとしたものは何？\\r"
"\nA. 棒だろ。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n人物1: 俺が木か聞いてみな。\\r"
"\n人物2: お前は木か？\\r"
"\n人物1: いいや。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nQ. レイヴンのどっち側に一番羽毛が生えてる？\\r"
"\nA. 外側。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nQ. 頭が3つあって、醜くて臭いものは何？\\r"
"\nA. おっと違った！ 君の頭は3つないな！\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nQ. 羽のように軽いけど、あまり長くは持たないものは何？\\r"
"\nA. 息。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nQ. スローターフィッシュがいるのにボートが沈みかけるのを想像して。どう助かる？\\r"
"\nA. 想像するのをやめる！\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nQ. なぜサンダーバグは生肉を食べるのか？\\r"
"\nA. 料理を習ったことがないから。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nQ. なぜハチはブンブン言うのか？\\r"
"\nA. 口笛が吹けないから。"

