#: 21337012-0-2701
msgctxt "21337012-0-2701"
msgid "Sir Marq,"
"\n"
"\nThe <<z:1>> of "High-King Emeric" is dead. It happened during the transfer. The wall crumbled and a troll grabbed the messenger. He was dead before he knew what was happening."
"\n"
"\nA High King allowing Orcs to rebuild Orsinium seems a great lie, but the messenger would not alter his story despite repeated questioning. With the messenger now dead, is there any hope of honorably ending our service?"
"\n"
"\nWhat hope is there for us now?"
"\n"
"\nVigilance eternal,"
"\nSir Emmath"
msgstr "マルク卿へ\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nエメリック上級王の<<1>>は死んだ。移送中に起こったことだ。壁が崩れ、使者はトロールに掴まれた。何が起こったか把握できる前に死んでいた。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n上級王がオークにオルシニウムを再建させるなど大きな嘘に思えるが、どれだけ問い詰めても使者は同じことしか言わなかった。使者が死んだ今、我々が立派に仕事を終えられる希望はないのだろうか？\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n我々に希望はあるのだろうか？\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n永遠の警戒を\\r"
"\nエマス卿"

